<example id="fs-idp156787120">
<para id="fs-idm55125200"><title>Umreikningur
þrýstingseininga</title>Bandaríska veðurstofan gefur upp
þrýsting bæði í tommum kvikasilfurs og millibörum. Reiknaðu um þrýsting
upp á 29,2 in. Hg í:</para>
<para id="fs-idp142663424">(a) torr</para>
<para id="fs-idp6847648">(b) atm</para>
<para id="fs-idm78213376">(c) kPa</para>
<para id="fs-idp62713296">(d) mbar</para>
<para id="fs-idp32588880"><title>Lausn</title>Þetta er verkefni um umreikning
eininga. Tengslin milli hinna ýmsu þrýstingseininga eru gefin í
<!-- XREF:6 -->.</para>
<para id="fs-idm19510112">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>29.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>in Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>25.4</m:mtext><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>in</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/>

<m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 torr</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/>

<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>742 torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para><para id="fs-idm103224224">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>742</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 atm</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>760</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0.976 atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp28156048">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>742</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>101.325 kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>760</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>98.9 kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm86928016">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>98.9</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>bar</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>100,000</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1000 mbar</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>bar</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>989 mbar</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm28185008"><title>Prófaðu þekkingu þína</title>Dæmigerður loftvogarþrýstingur í
Kansas City er 740 torr. Hver er þessi þrýstingur í loftþyngdum, í
millimetrum kvikasilfurs, í kílópaskölum og í börum?</para>
<note id="fs-idm54955856">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp131216672">0,974 atm; 740 mm Hg; 98,7 kPa;
0,987 bar</para>
</note>
</example>
<para id="fs-idm69336128">Við getum mælt loftþrýsting, kraftinn
sem lofthjúpurinn beitir á yfirborð jarðar, með <emphasis effect="bold">loftvog</emphasis>
(<!-- XREF:7 -->). Loftvog er glerpípa sem er lokuð í annan endann, fyllt með
órokgjörnum vökva eins og kvikasilfri og síðan hvolft og sökkt í ílát
með þeim vökva. Loftþrýstingurinn þrýstir á vökvann utan rörsins,
vökvasúlan þrýstir inni í rörinu og þrýstingurinn á yfirborði vökvans er
sá sami innan og utan rörsins. Hæð vökvans í rörinu er því í réttu
hlutfalli við þrýstinginn sem loftþrýstingurinn beitir.</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_09_01_Barometer" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idm35593680" alt="This figure shows two barometers. The barometer to the left contains a shallow reservoir, or open container, of mercury. A narrow tube extends upward from the reservoir above the reservoir. This tube is sealed at the top. To the right, a second similar setup is shown with a reservoir filled with water. Line segments connect the label “vacuum” to the tops of the two narrow tubes. The tube on the left shows the mercury in the reservoir extending in a column upward in the narrow tube. Similarly, the tube on the right shows the water in the reservoir extending upward into the related narrow tube. Double-headed arrows extend from the surface of each liquid in the reservoir to the top of the liquid in each tube. A narrow column or bar extends from the surface of the reservoir to the same height. This bar is labeled “atmospheric pressure.” The level of the water in its tube is significantly higher than the level of mercury in its tube.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_09_01_Barometer.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Í loftvog er
hæð, <emphasis effect="italics">h</emphasis>, vökvasúlunnar notuð sem mæling á loftþrýstingi. Með því að
nota mjög þéttan kvikasilfursvökva (til vinstri) er hægt að smíða
loftvogir af hæfilegri stærð, en ef notað væri vatn (til hægri) þyrfti
loftvog sem væri meira en 30 fet á hæð.</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idm79676464">Ef vökvinn er vatn mun venjulegur
loftþrýstingur halda uppi vatnssúlu sem er yfir 10 metra há, sem er
frekar óþægilegt til að smíða (og lesa af) loftvog. Þar sem kvikasilfur
(Hg) er um 13,6 sinnum þéttara en vatn þarf kvikasilfursloftvog aðeins
að vera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mn>13.6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> jafn há og vatnsloftvog – sem er hentugri stærð.
Staðlaður loftþrýstingur upp á 1 atm við sjávarmál (101.325 Pa)
samsvarar kvikasilfurssúlu sem er um 760 mm (29,92 tommur) á hæð.
<emphasis effect="bold">Torr</emphasis> var upphaflega ætlað að vera eining sem jafngildir einum
millimetra af kvikasilfri, en það samsvarar ekki lengur nákvæmlega.
Þrýstingurinn sem vökvi beitir vegna þyngdarafls er þekktur sem
<emphasis effect="bold">vökvastöðuþrýstingur</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="italics">p</emphasis>:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm35258720" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>h</m:mi><m:mi>ρ</m:mi><m:mi>g</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm61000288">þar sem <emphasis effect="italics">h</emphasis> er hæð vökvans, <emphasis effect="italics">ρ</emphasis>
(gríski lágstafurinn rhó) er eðlismassi vökvans og <emphasis effect="italics">g</emphasis> er hröðun vegna
þyngdarafls.</para>
<example id="fs-idm5509408">
<para id="fs-idm124424064"><title>Útreikningur á
loftvogarþrýstingi</title>Sýndu útreikninginn sem styður þá
fullyrðingu að loftþrýstingur nálægt sjávarmáli samsvari þrýstingnum sem
kvikasilfurssúla sem er um 760 mm á hæð beitir. Eðlismassi kvikasilfurs
= 13,6 g/cm<sup>3</sup>.</para>
<para id="fs-idm64631536"><title>Lausn</title>Vökvastöðuþrýstingur er gefinn með
<emphasis effect="italics">p</emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">hρg</emphasis>, þar sem <emphasis effect="italics">h</emphasis> = 760 mm, <emphasis effect="italics">ρ</emphasis> = 13,6 g/cm<sup>3</sup> og <emphasis effect="italics">g</emphasis> = 9,81
m/s<sup>2</sup>. Með því að setja þessi gildi inn í jöfnuna og framkvæma
nauðsynlegar einingabreytingar fáum við gildið sem við leitum að.
(Athugið: Við búumst við að finna þrýsting upp á ~101.325 Pa.)</para><equation id="fs-idm207611040" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>101,325</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>/m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>101,325</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>kg·m/s</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>m</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>101,325</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>kg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>m·s</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm149736288" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>760 mm</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>1000 mm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>13.6 g</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>cm</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 kg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>1000 g</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo> <m:mrow> <m:mtext>100 cm</m:mtext></m:mrow> <m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo> <m:mrow> <m:mtext>1 m</m:mtext></m:mrow> <m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>9.81 m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mtext>s</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm112352528" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>0.760 m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>13,600</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>kg/m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>9.81</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>m/s</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.01</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>kg/ms</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.01</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mtext>/m</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm93676560" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.01</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp70400640"><title>Prófaðu þekkingu þína</title>Reiknaðu hæð vatnssúlu við 25 °C sem
samsvarar venjulegum loftþrýstingi. Eðlismassi vatns við þetta hitastig
er 1,0 g/cm<sup>3</sup>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp73341600">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idp2146864">10,3 m</para>
</note>
</example>
<para id="fs-idp189718992"><emphasis effect="bold">Þrýstimælir</emphasis> er tæki svipað
loftvog sem hægt er að nota til að mæla þrýsting á gasi sem er lokað
inni í íláti. Þrýstimælir með lokuðum enda er U-laga rör með einum
lokuðum armi, einum armi sem tengist gasinu sem á að mæla og rokgjörnum
vökva (venjulega kvikasilfri) á milli. Eins og með loftvog er fjarlægðin
milli vökvayfirborðs í tveimur örmum rörsins (<emphasis effect="italics">h</emphasis> á skýringarmyndinni) í
réttu hlutfalli við þrýsting gassins í ílátinu. Þrýstimælir með opnum
enda (<!-- XREF:8 -->) er eins og þrýstimælir með lokuðum enda, en annar
armur hans er opinn út í andrúmsloftið. Í þessu tilviki samsvarar
fjarlægðin milli vökvayfirborðs muninum á þrýstingi milli gassins í
ílátinu og andrúmsloftsins.</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_09_01_Manometer" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idm5598960" alt="Three diagrams of manometers are shown. Each manometer consists of a spherical pink container filled with gas on the left that is connected to a U-shaped, sealed tube by a valve on its right. The top of the U aligns with the gas-filled sphere and the U, which extends below, contains mercury. The first manometer has a sealed tube. The sealed end to the upper right in the diagram is labeled “closed end” and “vacuum.” The mercury level is higher in the right side of the tube than in the left. The difference in height is labeled “h.” Beneath this manometer illustration appears the label P subscript gas equal sign h rho g. The second manometer has an open-ended tube, which is labeled “open end.” At this opening in the upper right of the diagram is the label P subscript atm. The mercury level is higher in the left side of the tube than in the right. This difference in height is labeled “h.” Beneath this manometer illustration appears the label P subscript gas equal sign P subscript atm minus sign h rho g. The third manometer has an open-ended tube and is similar to the second manometer except that the mercury level is higher in the right side of the tube than in the left. This difference in height is labeled “h.” Beneath this manometer illustration appears the label P subscript gas equal sign P subscript a t m plus h rho g.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_09_01_Manometer.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Hægt er að nota
þrýstimæli til að mæla þrýsting á gasi. (Munurinn á) hæð milli
vökvayfirborðs (<emphasis effect="italics">h</emphasis>) er mælikvarði á þrýstinginn. Kvikasilfur er
venjulega notað vegna mikils eðlismassa þess.</caption>
</figure>
<example id="fs-idm31201088">
<para id="fs-idp5332928"><title>Útreikningur á
þrýstingi með þrýstimæli með lokuðum enda</title>Þrýstingur gassýnis er mældur með
þrýstimæli með lokuðum enda, eins og sýnt er til hægri. Vökvinn í
þrýstimælinum er kvikasilfur. Ákvarðaðu þrýsting gassins í:</para>
<para id="fs-idp161989312">(a) torr</para>
<para id="fs-idp16104736">(b) Pa</para>
<para id="fs-idm85992448">(c) bar</para>
<media id="fs-idp141827632" class="scaled-down" alt="A diagram of a closed-end manometer is shown. To the upper left is a spherical container labeled, “gas.” This container is connected by a valve to a U-shaped tube which is labeled “closed end” at the upper right end. The container and a portion of tube that follows are shaded pink. The lower portion of the U-shaped tube is shaded grey with the height of the gray region being greater on the right side than on the left. The difference in height between the left side and right side is 26.4 c m which is indicated with horizontal line segments and arrows.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_09_01_Manometer1_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idm79648128"><title>Lausn</title>Þrýstingur gassins er jafn
kvikasilfurssúlu sem er 26,4 cm á hæð. (Þrýstingurinn við neðri láréttu
línuna er jafn báðum megin við rörið. Þrýstingurinn vinstra megin stafar
af gasinu og þrýstingurinn hægra megin stafar af 26,4 cm Hg, eða
kvikasilfri.) Við gætum notað jöfnuna <emphasis effect="italics">p</emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">hρg</emphasis> eins og í <!-- XREF:9 -->,
en það er einfaldara að breyta bara á milli eininga með því að nota
<!-- XREF:10 -->.</para>
<para id="fs-idm79108064">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>26.4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>cm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>cm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 torr</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>264 torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp62655904">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>264</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>760</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>torr</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>101,325 Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>35,200 Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2045200">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mtext>,200</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 bar</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>100,000</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>0.352 bar</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp37894320"><title>Prófaðu þekkingu þína</title>Þrýstingur gassýnis er mældur með
þrýstimæli með lokuðum enda. Vökvinn í þrýstimælinum er kvikasilfur.
Ákvarðaðu þrýsting gassins í:</para>
<para id="fs-idp38024128">(a) torr</para>
<para id="fs-idp16117232">(b) Pa</para>
<para id="fs-idp127919232">(c) bar</para>
<media id="fs-idp26163024" class="scaled-down" alt="A diagram of a closed-end manometer is shown. To the upper left is a spherical container labeled, “gas.” This container is connected by a valve to a U-shaped tube which is labeled “closed end” at the upper right end. The container and a portion of tube that follows are shaded pink. The lower portion of the U-shaped tube is shaded grey with the height of the gray region being greater on the right side than on the left. The difference in height of 6.0 i n is indicated with horizontal line segments and arrows.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_09_01_Manometer2_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<note id="fs-idm70430576">
<title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm8669760">(a) <sub>150 torr; (b) </sub>20.000 Pa; (c)
~0,20 bar</para>
</note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idm76587328">
<para id="fs-idm12992864"><title>Útreikningur á
þrýstingi með þrýstimæli með opnum enda</title>Þrýstingur gassýnis er mældur við
sjávarmál með Hg (kvikasilfurs) þrýstimæli með opnum enda, eins og sýnt
er til hægri. Ákvarðaðu þrýsting gassins í:</para>
<para id="fs-idp141807120">(a) mm Hg</para>
<para id="fs-idm91216192">(b) atm</para>
<para id="fs-idm29337808">(c) kPa</para>
<media id="fs-idp16540528" class="scaled-down" alt="A diagram of an opne-end manometer is shown. To the upper left is a spherical container labeled, “gas.” This container is connected by a valve to a U-shaped tube which is labeled “open end” at the upper right end. The container and a portion of tube that follows are shaded pink. The lower portion of the U-shaped tube is shaded grey with the height of the gray region being greater on the right side than on the left. The difference in height of 13.7 c m is indicated with horizontal line segments and arrows.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_09_01_Manometer3_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idp6251232"><title>Lausn</title>Þrýstingur gassins er jafn
vökvastöðuþrýstingi vegna kvikasilfurssúlu sem er 13,7 cm á hæð auk
loftþrýstings við sjávarmál. (Þrýstingurinn við neðri láréttu línuna er
jafn báðum megin í rörinu. Þrýstingurinn vinstra megin stafar af gasinu
og þrýstingurinn hægra megin stafar af 13,7 cm af Hg auk loftþrýstings.)</para>
<para id="fs-idp139076928">(a) Í mm Hg er þetta: 137 mm Hg +
760 mm Hg = 897 mm Hg</para>
<para id="fs-idm20839232">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>897</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>1 atm</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>760</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>mm Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.18 atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp8049056">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1.18</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>101.325 kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:menclose notation="horizontalstrike"><m:mrow><m:mtext>atm</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:menclose></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.20</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>kPa</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm24876576"><title>Prófaðu þekkingu þína</title>Þrýstingur gassýnis er mældur við
